Package: voiageR
Type: Package
Title: Value of Information Analysis in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: voiage Development Team
Maintainer: voiage Development Team <voiage@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: An R interface to the voiage Python library for Value of Information analysis. 
    Provides functions for calculating Expected Value of Perfect Information (EVPI), 
    Expected Value of Partial Perfect Information (EVPPI), and Expected Value of 
    Sample Information (EVSI).
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
SystemRequirements: Python (>= 3.8)
Imports:
    reticulate (>= 1.20)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
